The T-Rex has a goofy, endearing smile and wide, sparkling eyes that make it look as lovable as a playful dog. Beside it is its pterodactyl friend, lounging on a nearby rock with a laid-back smirk, casually smoking a joint as if resigned to the end of the world. The prehistoric setting features lush greenery and steaming volcanoes, but the sky is chaotic, filled with a plethora of smaller burning asteroids streaking down toward Earth, leaving fiery trails behind. The scene humorously juxtaposes the impending apocalypse with the duo’s carefree, almost comedic acceptance of their fate.”
